{
  "text": "Price for construction of PV solar power varies depending on the type of a plant, size, type of modules and equipment that is installed, etc. However, the price of PV modules (49%) has the greatest influence on the final value of the investment and depending on the material these prices vary. Within the total price, the value of building and construction works is about 29%, price of the inverter about 8% and the price of cables, switches and other electronic equipment around 7%. The remaining costs concern the documentation for the plant, the impact assessment study, connecting the local systems of electricity, taxes and utilities. On the other hand, costs for PV power plants maintenance are minimal [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
